target.title: Target
target.description: The Entity to follow, usually Player 1

distance.title: Distance
distance.description: How far the camera should be from the target entity

uiScreen.title: UI Screen Entity
uiScreen.description: The entity that handles the UI (gamePlay2DScreen) and should follow the camera at a specific distance

uiOffset.title: UI Offset
uiOffset.description: Relative offset position for the UI screen entity from the camera

finishLineEntity.title: Finish Line Entity
finishLineEntity.description: The entity representing the finish line.
